        ***** Menu Driven Program - Stack using Linked List *****

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 1

         Enter the number to be entered on the stack : 1

         |_1_| <- top
         -----

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 1

         Enter the number to be entered on the stack : 2

         |_2_| <- top
         |_1_|
         -----

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 1

         Enter the number to be entered on the stack : 3

         |_3_| <- top
         |_2_|
         |_1_|
         -----

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 1

         Enter the number to be entered on the stack : 4

         |_4_| <- top
         |_3_|
         |_2_|
         |_1_|
         -----

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 1

         Stack is full!

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 2

         |_3_| <- top
         |_2_|
         |_1_|
         -----

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 2

         |_2_| <- top
         |_1_|
         -----

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 2

         |_1_| <- top
         -----

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 2

         Stack is empty!

         1. Push
         2. Pop
         3. Exit

         Enter your choice : 3